extendedInfo.description: SunPass is the Florida Department ofTransportation's innovative PrepaidToll Program. Incorporating the latesttechnology, SunPass can be used onFlorida's toll roads and most toll bridges.SunPass customers typically pay 25 centsless than cash customers at most tollplazas and exits on Turnpike roads.

reviews.title: Slapped mobile site in it
reviews.comment: This is more like a shortcut to the mobile version of the Sunpass site. Make a real app with native controls and not just an embedded webview.  Also, changing language throws an Apache error. Going back does show the content in the selected language though.  Add a feature: next rest area, gas station near exit, or similar.  And on the site: allow to pay paper invoices with transponder balance.
reviews.author: Mando Padilla

reviews.title: Stop Bitching
reviews.comment: It works. I created an account. I added a transponder.  I put money in my account. I saw my history.  Whether it\'s a shortcut or not...  It works. Whether the GUI is up to your standards is irrelevant. Get over it.  It does what it is supposed to do. If it doesn\'t,  you most likely have a sucky connection or phone. Deal with it.  Lol.  It works perfectly fine.
